I wonder what risks does we early cryptocurrency adopters have in next 5-10 years?
does anyone thinks that some future project comes along and dominates more than bitcoin, komodo, eth?
like if some government or some big company issues their project and puts more developer efforts to it, it will be risk to value of existing cryptocurrency projects like the ones I mentioned?
